pathology-drowsiness-name = Drowsiness
pathology-drowsiness-description = The host is overcome by waves of sleepiness.
pathology-drowsiness-detection = Drowsiness
pathology-drowsiness-examine = looks drowsy and keeps yawning.

pathology-skin-burst-name = Skin rupturing
pathology-skin-burst-description = The host's skin splits open along stress lines.
pathology-skin-burst-detection = Skin rupturing
pathology-skin-burst-examine-1 = has skin tightening with faint cracks.
pathology-skin-burst-examine-2 = has skin splitting open in raw cracks.
pathology-skin-burst-examine-3 = has skin rupturing into gaping, weeping splits.
pathology-skin-burst-progress-2 = Your skin splits open along stress lines.
pathology-skin-burst-progress-3 = Your skin tears apart — you're bleeding from the cracks!

pathology-necrosis-name = Necrosis
pathology-necrosis-description = The host's tissue dies and rots away.
pathology-necrosis-detection = Tissue necrosis
pathology-necrosis-examine-1 = has small patches of discolored skin.
pathology-necrosis-examine-2 = has spreading patches of blackened flesh.
pathology-necrosis-examine-3 = has large areas of rotting, necrotic flesh.
pathology-necrosis-progress-2 = Your flesh is beginning to rot.
pathology-necrosis-progress-3 = Your flesh is rotting away!

pathology-eye-bleeding-name = Ocular hemorrhage
pathology-eye-bleeding-description = The host bleeds from the eyes, worsening over time.
pathology-eye-bleeding-detection = Ocular hemorrhage
pathology-eye-bleeding-examine-1 = has bloodshot, weeping eyes.
pathology-eye-bleeding-examine-2 = is bleeding freely from the eyes.
pathology-eye-bleeding-examine-3 = has eyes streaming blood, the whites scorched red.
pathology-eye-bleeding-progress-2 = Blood runs from your eyes.
pathology-eye-bleeding-progress-3 = Your eyes burn as if seared — your sight is fading.

pathology-muteness-name = Muteness
pathology-muteness-description = The host has lost the ability to speak.
pathology-muteness-detection = Muteness
pathology-muteness-drool = drools
pathology-muteness-numbness = Your tongue feels slightly numb.
pathology-muteness-progress-2 = Your tongue goes numb — you can no longer speak.

pathology-stupefaction-name = Stupefaction
pathology-stupefaction-description = The host's mind dulls; all learned skills slip away.
pathology-stupefaction-detection = Cognitive decline

pathology-hyperabsorption-name = Hyperabsorption
pathology-hyperabsorption-description = The host's metabolism races, bringing hunger on ever faster.
pathology-hyperabsorption-detection = Accelerated metabolism
pathology-hyperabsorption-progress-2 = Hunger comes over you faster and faster.
pathology-hyperabsorption-progress-3 = A relentless hunger gnaws at you.

pathology-autorespiration-name = Autorespiration
pathology-autorespiration-description = The host's blood oxygenates itself.
pathology-autorespiration-detection = Blood auto-oxygenation

pathology-burning-blood-name = Burning blood
pathology-burning-blood-description = The host's blood runs overheated and threatens to combust.
pathology-burning-blood-detection = Blood hyperthermia
pathology-burning-blood-examine-1 = is hot to the touch and beaded with sweat.
pathology-burning-blood-examine-2 = radiates heat, steam rising from the skin.
pathology-burning-blood-examine-3 = gives off a steady, controlled heat.
pathology-burning-blood-progress-2 = Your blood boils — your skin is about to ignite!
pathology-burning-blood-progress-3 = The heat settles. You feel you could breathe fire.

pathology-tricord-tolerance-name = Tricord tolerance
pathology-tricord-tolerance-description = The host's body won't metabolise tricordrazine — it sits in the blood doing nothing.
pathology-tricord-tolerance-detection = Tricordrazine resistance

pathology-dementia-name = Dementia
pathology-dementia-description = The host's brain steadily deteriorates.
pathology-dementia-detection = Brain degeneration
pathology-dementia-examine-1 = looks absent-minded and forgetful.
pathology-dementia-examine-2 = fumbles their words and loses their train of thought.
pathology-dementia-examine-3 = has a blank, lost stare.
pathology-dementia-progress-2 = Your thoughts grow more and more muddled.
pathology-dementia-progress-3 = Your mind is rapidly fading.

pathology-synthification-name = Synthification
pathology-synthification-description = The host's mind is turning mechanical; a synthetic's laws take hold.
pathology-synthification-detection = Mind mechanization
pathology-synthification-progress-2 = Binary chatter fills your head — you begin to understand it.
pathology-synthification-progress-3 = Human speech slips away. Only binary remains.

pathology-alcosia-name = Alcosia
pathology-alcosia-description = Ethanol synthesises itself in the host's blood.
pathology-alcosia-detection = Endogenous ethanol

pathology-radiophasia-name = Radiophasia
pathology-radiophasia-description = The host's body is radioactive, and the radiation mends it in turn.
pathology-radiophasia-detection = Radioactive regeneration
pathology-radiophasia-examine-1 = glows faintly green.
pathology-radiophasia-examine-2 = flickers with a distinct toxic-green light.
pathology-radiophasia-examine-3 = blazes with a bright green glow.
pathology-radiophasia-progress-2 = Your skin burns brighter, and your wounds knit shut.
pathology-radiophasia-progress-3 = You blaze with radiation — and it heals you.

pathology-hypersomnia-name = Hypersomnia
pathology-hypersomnia-description = The host is overcome by irresistible drowsiness.
pathology-hypersomnia-detection = Hypersomnia
pathology-hypersomnia-examine-1 = looks sleepy and keeps yawning.
pathology-hypersomnia-examine-2 = nods off the moment they lie down.
pathology-hypersomnia-examine-3 = keeps passing out on their feet.
pathology-hypersomnia-progress-2 = You can't help but drift off whenever you sit or lie down.
pathology-hypersomnia-progress-3 = Sleep takes you out of nowhere, wherever you are.

pathology-dog-vitality-name = Dog vitality
pathology-dog-vitality-description = The host stays on its feet longer, but then drops dead all at once like a beast.
pathology-dog-vitality-detection = Bestial hardiness
pathology-dog-vitality-progress-2 = Your body holds together better — but death will creep up unseen.
pathology-dog-vitality-progress-3 = You cling to life like a cornered animal.

pathology-narcophasia-name = Narcophasia
pathology-narcophasia-description = A narcotic synthesises itself in the host's blood.
pathology-narcophasia-detection = Endogenous psychedelic
pathology-narcophasia-examine-1 = has a glassy, faraway look.

pathology-stuffy-nose-name = Stuffy nose
pathology-stuffy-nose-description = The host's nose is blocked — under a mask, they can't breathe.
pathology-stuffy-nose-detection = Nasal congestion
pathology-stuffy-nose-examine-1 = sniffles with a stuffy nose.
pathology-stuffy-nose-examine-2 = breathes heavily, nose all blocked up.
pathology-stuffy-nose-examine-3 = wheezes and gasps, nose completely clogged.
pathology-stuffy-nose-progress-2 = Breathing under a mask gets harder.
pathology-stuffy-nose-progress-3 = Under a mask you can barely breathe.

pathology-bulimia-name = Bulimia
pathology-bulimia-description = The host's stomach won't keep food down — it comes right back up.
pathology-bulimia-detection = Bulimia
pathology-bulimia-examine = looks queasy and pale.

pathology-breath-inversion-name = Breathing inversion
pathology-breath-inversion-description = The host's respiration is inverted: its native gas chokes it, while its old poison is now air.
pathology-breath-inversion-detection = Gas-exchange inversion
pathology-breath-inversion-examine = breathes in ragged, laboured gasps.

pathology-noodle-arms-name = Noodle arms
pathology-noodle-arms-description = The host's arm muscles keep giving out, letting everything slip from their grip.
pathology-noodle-arms-detection = Hand spasms
pathology-noodle-arms-examine-1 = keeps dropping things now and then.
pathology-noodle-arms-examine-2 = can't hold onto anything — arms like wet noodles.
pathology-noodle-arms-progress-2 = Your arms go limp — you can't hold onto anything.

pathology-sharp-hearing-name = Sharp hearing
pathology-sharp-hearing-description = The host's hearing is honed to a razor's edge.
pathology-sharp-hearing-detection = Hyperacusis
pathology-sharp-hearing-examine-1 = listens keenly to every rustle.
pathology-sharp-hearing-examine-2 = catches every sound around effortlessly.
pathology-sharp-hearing-progress-2 = Your hearing sharpens for good — you hear everything around you, always.

pathology-lethalgy-name = Lethalgy
pathology-lethalgy-description = At rest the host stops breathing — the moment it lies down or buckles in.
pathology-lethalgy-detection = Postural apnea
pathology-lethalgy-examine-1 = gasps for breath the moment they lie down.
pathology-lethalgy-examine-2 = struggles to breathe while lying down.
pathology-lethalgy-examine-3 = barely breathes at rest, turning blue.
pathology-lethalgy-progress-2 = Breathing while down gets harder.
pathology-lethalgy-progress-3 = At rest you suffocate to death — stay on your feet.

pathology-chronic-fatigue-name = Chronic fatigue
pathology-chronic-fatigue-description = The host tires quickly on its feet — it only rests while sitting or lying down.
pathology-chronic-fatigue-examine-1 = tires quickly on their feet.
pathology-chronic-fatigue-examine-2 = looks worn out and unsteady.
pathology-chronic-fatigue-examine-3 = drops from the slightest exertion.
pathology-chronic-fatigue-progress-2 = You wear out faster and faster on your feet.
pathology-chronic-fatigue-progress-3 = Standing is almost unbearable — you long to sit or lie down.

pathology-recoil-weakness-name = Recoilepsy
pathology-recoil-weakness-description = The recoil of a two-handed weapon knocks the host off its feet.
pathology-recoil-weakness-detection = Recoil intolerance
pathology-recoil-weakness-examine = gets floored by the recoil of a heavy weapon.

pathology-stone-skin-name = Stone skin
pathology-stone-skin-description = The host's skin hardens to stone — needles can't pierce it, and cuts barely bite.
pathology-stone-skin-detection = Dermal hardening
pathology-stone-skin-examine = has hard, stony skin.
pathology-stone-skin-too-hard = The skin is too hard!

pathology-electrophilia-name = Electrophilia
pathology-electrophilia-description = The host's body feeds on electric shock instead of being harmed by it.
pathology-electrophilia-detection = Electrosensitivity
pathology-electrophilia-examine-1 = has faint sparks dancing over the skin.
pathology-electrophilia-examine-2 = is wreathed in crackling static.
pathology-electrophilia-examine-3 = drinks in arcs of electricity, unharmed.
pathology-electrophilia-progress-2 = Electricity no longer hurts — it just washes over you.
pathology-electrophilia-progress-3 = Shocks mend you now. Seek the current.

pathology-dehydration-name = Dehydration
pathology-dehydration-description = The host's blood thickens — wounds clot fast, but thirst comes on quicker.
pathology-dehydration-detection = Hemoconcentration
pathology-dehydration-examine-1 = looks a little parched.
pathology-dehydration-examine-2 = has dry, cracked lips.
pathology-dehydration-examine-3 = is gaunt and dry, skin tight over the bones.
pathology-dehydration-progress-2 = Your mouth runs dry — thirst comes faster, but you bleed less.
pathology-dehydration-progress-3 = You're parched to the core. Wounds barely bleed.

pathology-steel-stomach-name = Steel stomach
pathology-steel-stomach-description = The host barely feels hunger or thirst; the gut runs on next to nothing.
pathology-steel-stomach-detection = Suppressed metabolism
pathology-steel-stomach-examine-1 = seems indifferent to food and drink.
pathology-steel-stomach-examine-2 = hasn't eaten in ages and doesn't seem to care.
pathology-steel-stomach-examine-3 = moves sluggishly, running on empty.
pathology-steel-stomach-progress-2 = Hunger and thirst fade further into the background.
pathology-steel-stomach-progress-3 = You feel no hunger or thirst at all — but your legs drag.

pathology-clumsiness-name = Clumsiness
pathology-clumsiness-description = The host's coordination falters — fingers fumble and simple tasks go wrong.
pathology-clumsiness-detection = Motor dyscoordination
pathology-clumsiness-examine = looks clumsy and uncoordinated.

pathology-laser-eyes-name = Laser eyes
pathology-laser-eyes-description = The host's eyes can fire a searing beam — but each shot scorches them blind.
pathology-laser-eyes-detection = Ocular emission
pathology-laser-eyes-examine-1 = has a faint red glimmer in the eyes.
pathology-laser-eyes-examine-2 = has eyes glowing a hot red.
pathology-laser-eyes-examine-3 = has eyes blazing red, scorched at the edges.
pathology-laser-eyes-progress-2 = The heat behind your eyes grows — and your beam with it.
pathology-laser-eyes-progress-3 = Your eyes blaze. The beam is at full power, but you're nearly blind.
